# Complete GitHub CLI Commands Reference

## Introduction

GitHub CLI (`gh`) is the official command-line tool for GitHub that brings pull requests, issues, and other GitHub concepts to your terminal. This reference covers all available commands as of February 2025.

## Installation

```bash
# macOS
brew install gh

# Windows
winget install --id GitHub.cli

# Debian/Ubuntu
apt install gh

# Fedora/CentOS
dnf install gh
```

